Jovanice Twinobusingye bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Ugandan, onye omeiwu na onye nnọchi anya nwanyị nke ndị omeiwu maka Kiruhura District na nke iri na otu nke Uganda. Ọ bụ onye otu National Resistance Movement (NRM). Ọ na-anọdụ na Kọmitii Ndị Omeiwu na Ọrụ Ọha na Gọọmentị Obodo nke Hon

Mary Begumisa meriri Twinobusingye na asọmpi maka tiketi NRM maka Sembabule Woman onye otu oche ndị omeiwu.  O meriri na ntuli aka NRM site na imeri Nuweahereza Phionah na Mwiine Sheillah ka ọ bụrụ onye na-ebu ọkọlọtọ NRM na ntuliaka mba na afo puku abụọ na iri abụọ na otu Twinobusingye meriri na ntuli aka mba nke 2021 iji bụrụ onye nnọchi anya nwanyị nke ndị omeiwu maka Kiruhura District na nke iri na otu nke Uganda.
Twinobusingye bụ akụkụ nke isi Rabecca Kadaga mgbe ọ malitere itinye akwụkwọ maka oge nke atọ n'ọfịs n'oge mkpọsa ntuli aka ya na Speke Resort, Munyonyo na Kampala.

Twinobusingye so n'ime ndị omeiwu nke Uganda bụ ndị katọrọ ọnọdụ ọjọọ nke okporo ụzọ na mpaghara ya mgbe ndị omeiwu na-arụrịta ụka banyere mmegharị ahụ na-agba gọọmentị ume ka ha gbasie mbọ ịkwalite nchekwa okporo ụzọ nke Alex Ruhunda kpaliri, n'oge ncheta nke National Road Safety Week
O kwuru na ya nwere ụzọ ọjọọ n'ihi obere mmefu ego nke Ministry of Works and Transport.
Twinobusingye jụrụ nsonaazụ ntuli aka nke 2020 NRM primaries mgbe Mary Begumisa meriri ya na asọmpi maka tiketi NRM maka Sembabule Woman onye otu oche ndị omeiwu

Joy Kabasti onye jụkwara otu nsonaazụ ahụ kwuru na a tọọrọ ọtụtụ ndị na-edeba aha na mpaghara ruo ọtụtụ awa ka ha na-eziga ụdị nkwupụta ahụ na ụlọ ọrụ ndekọ distrikti na-ekwu na ọ nweghị ụzọ nsonaazụ ga-esi bụrụ ihe a pụrụ ịdabere na ya.

Twinobusingye so n'ime mmadụ anọ n'ime ndị asaa na-azọ ọkwa.National Resistance Movement primaries na Mawogola North na West constituencies, Sembabule District bụ ndị jụrụ iji National Identity Cards na 2020 NRM primaries dị ka guildline nke Tanga Odoi nyere ebe ndị niile na-atụ vootu ga-egosi kaadị National Identification ha tupu ha enwee ike ịtụ vootu maka onye ha. Odoi kwuru na kọmitii ahụ bu n'uche ịtọpụta njirimara doro anya maka ndị na-eme ntụli aka ziri ezi maka ebumnuche nke iwepụ ndị na-abụghị ndị bi na ya nwere ike ịbanye ma ọ bụ jiri nzuzo weta n'ógbè ahụ iji chịkwaa usoro ahụ ma o kwuru na iji IDs ga-egbochi ọtụtụ ndị si na mpaghara ndị ọzọ ịtụ vootu

Twinobusingye nyere ihe abụọ mere ọ jụrụ, otu bụ na ọtụtụ ndị na-eme ntụli aka efunahụla kaadị ma ọ bụ debanye aha mana ha ahọrọbeghị ha site na National Identification and Registration Authority- NIRA
Ihe nke abụọ kpatara ya bụ na ụfọdụ ndị na-eme ntụli aka n'ógbè ahụ ghọgburu ọtụtụ ndị na-atụ vootu ka ha tụfuo kaadị ha dị ka ndị nchebe mgbe ha nwetara aka azụ.
